{"TopicId":193811,"ForumId":24,"TopicTitle":"How do i post a picture","CreatedByName":"JcoolTheShipbuilder","CreatedById":204576,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-05-12T14:49:48Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"JcoolTheShipbuilder","CreatedById":204576,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-05-12T14:49:48Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI want to post a pic on a topic about what i did in ksp today, but then i realized that i dont know how to post pics directly from my pc. is it possible to post a pic directly from pc, or do i have to upload it first?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"VoidCosmos","CreatedById":192336,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-05-12T15:12:38Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223784162\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022193811\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221589294988\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022204576\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022JcoolTheShipbuilder\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n22 minutes ago, JcoolTheShipbuilder said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI want to post a pic on a topic about what i did in ksp today, but then i realized that i dont know how to post pics directly from my pc. is it possible to post a pic directly from pc, or do i have to upload it first?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHi and welcome to the Forum! Maybe this can help you:\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedauthorid=\u0022179753\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed7168910197\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/173756-quick-guide-to-posting-pictures-on-the-forum/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022 style=\u0022height:211px;max-width:502px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"JcoolTheShipbuilder","CreatedById":204576,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-05-12T16:13:05Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223784176\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022193811\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221589296358\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022192336\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022VoidCosmos\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n57 minutes ago, VoidCosmos said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHi and welcome to the Forum! Maybe this can help you:\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedauthorid=\u0022179753\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed5868821213\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/173756-quick-guide-to-posting-pictures-on-the-forum/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022 style=\u0022height:211px;max-width:502px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nwell... for some reason, when i tried it with the imigur, i made the post, copied the link, but when i tried clicking on \u0022insert image from URL\u0022 here, the input box just turns red?\u003Cbr\u003E\nalso, do i have to make an account there to save the posts so i can post the pics here?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Vanamonde","CreatedById":27914,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-05-12T16:25:51Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe insert image method is more complex than you need. Just copy/paste Imgur\u0027s BBCode link into your post as text. When you hit the submit button, the forum software will automatically convert it into the picture to be displayed.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd welcome to the forum. \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"JcoolTheShipbuilder","CreatedById":204576,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-05-12T16:32:52Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nwhats the BBCode link? the one where you hover over the image and click copy for?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://imgur.com/W04hMWu\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://imgur.com/W04hMWu\u003C/a\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nok, i tried it\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nhmmm.....\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://imgur.com/a/UxfjE3v\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://imgur.com/a/UxfjE3v\u003C/a\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222020-05-12T16:37:09Z\u0022 title=\u002205/12/2020 04:37  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00224 yr\u0022\u003EMay 12, 2020\u003C/time\u003E by JcoolTheShipbuilder\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"VoidCosmos","CreatedById":192336,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-05-12T16:45:51Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSo, when you click on the link you have provided, right-click the picture an click on the open in new tab. Then copy the link from the search box and paste it directly into your post. Wait for a second or two and it should embed into your post\n\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022W04hMWu.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002256.25\u0022 height=\u0022576\u0022 width=\u00221024\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/W04hMWu.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt should appear like that\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Vanamonde","CreatedById":27914,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-05-12T22:36:14Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis code, copied from Imgur,\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 alt=\u0022YSQ7cfa.png\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/YSQ7cfa.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nbecomes the actual pic when submitted.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"JcoolTheShipbuilder","CreatedById":204576,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-05-13T03:27:41Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022W04hMWu.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002256.25\u0022 height=\u0022576\u0022 width=\u00221024\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/W04hMWu.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nohhhh ok\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nthanks!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222020-05-13T03:27:53Z\u0022 title=\u002205/13/2020 03:27  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00224 yr\u0022\u003EMay 13, 2020\u003C/time\u003E by JcoolTheShipbuilder\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Superfluous J","CreatedById":73725,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-05-13T04:40:55Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou can also while viewing imgur, right click your picture and \u0022copy image location\u0022 or whatever your browser uses for that type of link (that\u0027s Firefox).\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThen paste the image link here and it\u0027ll show up for a second as text, then turn into the image.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAlso, cool ship!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"VoidCosmos","CreatedById":192336,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-05-13T06:25:03Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223784476\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022193811\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221589340461\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022204576\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022JcoolTheShipbuilder\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 hours ago, JcoolTheShipbuilder said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/W04hMWu.jpg\u0022 title=\u0022Enlarge image\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022W04hMWu.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage ipsImage_thumbnailed\u0022 data-ratio=\u002256.25\u0022 height=\u0022576\u0022 width=\u00221024\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/W04hMWu.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nohhhh ok\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nthanks!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI like the ship!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}